channeldata.description: PlantUML is a component that allows to quickly write:    - Sequence diagram,   - Use case diagram,   - Class diagram,   - Activity diagram,   - Component diagram,   - State diagram,   - Object diagram,   - Deployment diagram,   - Timing diagram  And also:    - Activity diagram (legacy syntax)   - Archimate diagram   - Gantt charts   - SALT UI mockups  Furthermore:    - Hyperlinks and tooltips   - Creole: rich text, emoticons, unicode, icons   - OpenIconic icons   - Sprite icons   - AsciiMath mathematical expressions  To know more about PlantUML, please visit http://plantuml.com/
channeldata.summary: Generate UML diagram from textual description
